# WellPro Codebase Cleanup and Optimization

This plan addresses the syntax errors and contamination in the project files resulting from recent copy-pasted content. We will purify the code while maintaining all the visual and functional logic you've added.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Some components (Navbar, Hero, Pricing) reference a `Button` component in `src/components/ui/button.jsx` which currently does not exist. I will create a high-quality, reusable Button component to resolve these errors.

## Proposed Changes

### UI Components

#### [NEW] [button.jsx](file:///Users/viveksuyal/Downloads/wellpro/frontend/src/components/ui/button.jsx)
- Create a flexible, Tailwind-powered Button component with multiple variants (primary, outline, etc.) to support the existing section code.

### Section Cleanups

I will process each for the following:
- Remove strings like `Action: file_editor...`, `Observation: ...`, and surrounding quotes.
- Unescape all characters (e.g., change `\"` back to `"`).
- Fix minor syntax errors introduced during pasting (e.g., `div className =\"...\"` -> `<div className="..."`).
- Ensure all sections are correctly exported for `App.jsx`.

